sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant UI as UserInput
    participant R as Resume
    participant FH as FileHandler
    U->>UI: fill out resume form
    UI->>R: create Resume object
    R->>FH: save_to_word()
    FH-->>U: return Word document
    R->>FH: save_to_pdf()
    FH-->>U: return PDF document